OL,3,CGuernsey police launch campaign to
OL,4,Cencourage more locals to join the force
OL,6,FGuernsey Police have launched a
OL,7,Fcampaign to encourage more locals to
OL,8,Fjoin the force.
OL,10,FIt uses footage from body cameras worn
OL,11,Fby serving officers to give
OL,12,Fprospective recruits an idea of what
OL,13,Fit's like to be in the service.
OL,15,FThose successful would be able to
OL,16,Ftrain and become police constables on-
OL,17,Fisland in Guernsey.
