OL,3,CGuernsey police launch campaign to
OL,4,Cencourage more locals to join the force
OL,6,FChief Inspector Liam Johnson said:
OL,7,F"This latest recruitment campaign is
OL,8,Fas real as it can get, as we have used
OL,9,Fcensored, real body-worn camera
OL,10,Ffootage from the last 12 months of
OL,11,Fpolice work.
OL,13,F"We decided there was no better way to
OL,14,Fshow the community what it is we do to
OL,15,Fserve Guernsey and its community.
OL,17,F"There are many assumptions about what
OL,18,Fit is to be a police officer, and
OL,19,Fwhile dealing with criminals and
OL,20,Foffences is a big part of it, it is
OL,21,Fonly one piece of the puzzle.
