OL,3,CGuernsey police launch campaign to
OL,4,Cencourage more locals to join the force
OL,6,F"Our officers respond to a huge range
OL,7,Fof incidents and need to be there for
OL,8,Fpeople in many different situations `
OL,9,Fthe driving force for that is that we
OL,10,Fall do this job to help people and
OL,11,Fmake the community a better place.
OL,13,F"The next round of recruits will be
OL,14,Fstarting their on-island training
OL,15,Fearly next year, and we're looking for
OL,16,Fapplicants who have good people
OL,17,Fskills, a passion for helping others,
OL,18,Fand a dedication to this community."
